{"tid":1487953,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(齊來撚蝗) 墨爾本大學留學生 IG中指公開侮辱集會港人 自爆包圍港狗期間高歌Made In China心情舒暢","createTime":"2019-08-19T12:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T06:30:46.000Z","uid":243762,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2061b1130f8e4dd5e55480e63be6c7c1e484f53f","tid":1487953,"uid":243762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:57:42.000Z","msg":"大家都知道上禮拜喺Melbourne 有手足俾人 包圍<br />\n啲質素就唔使再多講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有人被捕正在開啟遣返程序正式柒出國際<br />\n點知今日開IG嘅時候 仲見到有蝗喺度打緊飛機<br />\n一開始以為係啲普通5毛 睇真啲屌啊原來exchange嗰陣見過依個蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係自由社會唔使翻牆上美帝ig<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲公然侮辱民主唔使付出代價？ </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果贊成會出埋樣俾大家睇下 （大量）</span><br />\n典型支那紅衛兵樣唔做軍妓真係嘥曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成撚日又13億又吹到千幾人包圍好撚巴閉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一人一句叫下面依幾隻蝗躝返去微博睇人民日報 <br />\n比佢哋知道狗係唔可以用人嘅apps <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">IG: lyfbenren (Faye Li)<br />\nUniversity of Melbourne</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gBXkkUr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgBXkkUr.png&h=aad7ed12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T5pKNzv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT5pKNzv.png&h=52305f6c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cis4Nzw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCis4Nzw.png&h=14913311&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yaoPeey.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyaoPeey.png&h=0f225c21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好話佢哋係俾人煽動 想同呢班成個腦得殖民主義嘅蝗溝通？未開口就已經屌曬你全家</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N8pZCu6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN8pZCu6.png&h=cd3b4462&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">圖三留言者 Minty Li</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ugRtvU5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FugRtvU5.png&h=a56bf4f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n題外話 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢隻蝗同佢啲朋友據聞由中學(middle school)開始已經喺度做留學生 咁撚多年個腦都仲係裝緊屎 狗改不了吃屎是真的</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a07bc0d4d1a3db5bfe432b537d6740cf5c48b51","tid":1487953,"uid":293667,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Oo6k5U5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOo6k5U5.gif&h=55054061&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[文宣組注意 幫推]8.18後又是新開始 工作又要重新開始了 繼續撕一貼十精神<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487760\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487760</a>"},{"pid":"b838090394d4a1f676c5159bd12d23b45f830e0a","tid":1487953,"uid":243762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:01:16.000Z","msg":"Pus